data.description: This a show stopper, a must see stunning home with plenty of space. The kitchen has a center island and beautiful backsplash, making the ideal spot for gathering with family and friends. This beautiful home has coffered ceilings, and tons of room for entertaining. The owners suite is a true retreat including double vanity, separate shower and tub. The backyard is the perfect area for entertaining with a lavish in ground pool. This house is ready for the taking. Come see and don't let his beauty get away. Schedule a showing today!
